questions.guide_to_inspection:
Compressors, pumps and fuel supply should be arranged for manual remote emergency stop from the following locations as
applicable:
> navigation bridge;
> cargo control room;
> onboard safety center;
> engine control room;
> fire-control station; and
> adjacent to the exit of fuel preparation rooms.
(MSC.1-Circ.1687, Interim Guidelines For the safety of Ships Using Ammonia as Fuel 2025)

